    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Octopress Blogging Workflow]]></title>
    <link href="http://sookoor.github.io/blog/octopress-blogging-workflow/"/>
    <updated>2014-06-13T09:57:43-05:00</updated>
    <id>http://sookoor.github.io/blog/octopress-blogging-workflow</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Create a new post: <code>rake new_post[&lt;Title&gt;]</code>  </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Add content by editing <code>source/_posts/&lt;date&gt;-&lt;Title&gt;.markdown</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>Preview changes:
    <ul>
      <li>If using <a href="http://pow.cx">Pow</a>, run <code>rake generate</code> and open <a href="http://octopress.dev">octopress.dev</a> in a browser</li>
      <li>Otherwise, run <code>rake preview</code> and open [localhost:4000](localhost:4000] in a browser</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Publish post and push changes to Github:      </p>

    <pre><code> rake generate
 rake deploy
 git add .
 git commit -am "&lt;commit message&gt;"
 git push origin source
</code></pre>
  </li>
</ol>
]]></content>
